stock_count_entry_screen.dart — the core new screen:
Header: Location, Count Date, category-subtree picker (adapt product_entry_screen.dart's _buildCategoryPicker — flat Autocomplete<ItemCategoryModel> over precomputed breadcrumb paths — made nullable, "All Categories" default; the picked value is the subtree root, expanded server-side via fn_category_subtree), nature filter (adapt product_list_screen.dart's _NatureFilter dropdown pattern, nullable = "All Natures").
