Scan-to-jump: gated by session.enableBarcode/enablePartNumber. onFieldSubmitted does a local lookup against the already-loaded worksheet (never remote — the worksheet is a closed universe once started), scrolls to and highlights the matching row, autofocuses its qty field. No match → clear snackbar, not a silent no-op.
